{"tid":629791,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"傳Ofo擬收購GoBee.Bike","createTime":"2018-04-15T04:12:23.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-15T05:14:01.000Z","uid":113000,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"b9646a5faa7a13c610193d5c30f1af93758fba5c","tid":629791,"uid":113000,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-15T04:12:23.000Z","msg":"本地傳媒引述消息指，內地共享單車Ofo計劃收購本港同業GoBee.Bike。<br />\n<br />\n消息指，Ofo會接手營運GoBee.Bike，未有透露財務資料，短期內會維持它的品牌，但有關洽購處於初步階段，最後或未能達成協議。<br />\n<br />\nGoBee.Bike為本港首間提供共享單車服務的公司，在新界提供約400輛單車。<span style=\"color: red;\">GoBee.Bike去年8月完成首輪融資，由Grishin Robotic領投及阿里巴巴香港創業者基金參與投資，獲得逾900萬美元（7,020萬港元）。</span><br />\n<br />\nOfo上月公布，完成E2-1輪融資，規模達8.66億美元，該輪融資由阿里牽頭。<br />\n<br />\n消息指，Ofo與GoBee.Bike合作有道理，<span style=\"color: red;\">因兩公司背後都是阿里的生態系統，而本港只有少數共享單車公司。</span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://invest.hket.com/article/2049615/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Finvest.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2049615%2F&d=e2PC5uQKZy0AmFTAHjyWpozu7PIJYhBZqlGrkalTKs4%3D&h=de799766\" target=\"_blank\">http://invest.hket.com/article/2049615/</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d0308986d583192094cd6c1eca1de06e6c79b3fb","tid":629791,"uid":157362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-15T04:14:21.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e144929a11a7ac5c82758d8f113141cd1bc7b52c","tid":629791,"uid":41245,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-15T04:18:26.000Z","msg":"咪又係一街垃圾單車<br />\n以佢地嘅business model，根本做唔到有服務有保養維修又收支平衡"},{"pid":"8aef944708ca797b82f76a397a7d01e0f45c51c9","tid":629791,"uid":5843,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"e144929a11a7ac5c82758d8f113141cd1bc7b52c","tid":629791,"uid":41245,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-15T04:18:26.000Z","msg":"咪又係一街垃圾單車<br />\n以佢地嘅business model，根本做唔到有服務有保養維修又收支平衡"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-15T04:27:23.000Z","msg":"佢地目標係用平價殺哂同行，再慢慢壟斷上去"},{"pid":"7c1